This tool is suitable for Windows platform. You can insert your own USB and prepare the Macintosh system image. Right click "ddmac.exe" and click "run as administrator". After opening, click three points to select your system image. Then cancel the three function buttons, and then click "write" to start writing. If the log column says "finish" and "all done, have fun!" it means that the image has been written to USB, and you can start it with the USB drive!
Note: if there is no Macintosh system image, here is~
Website: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1SkV0gq3Xh1TjsOMaU8nDnQ
Extraction code: 2tqk
Having fun！！
